        "text": "several times. One I remember, it was when I was like still young, I was maybe fifteen and I was supposed to go to a friend's house just to sleep, but in fact I just went to a party with some friends and I drank some alcohol and then we got caught by the police so I had to lie to my mother I'm afraid. After that she had been aware of this like two weeks after maybe and it was like a really bad moment for me."
