        "text": "Stuff like that.  The ones that, just really simplistic ones, things like Tetris and putting squares in boxes and Bejeweled where you change, moving things around.  Those kind of games I can get very readily addicted to so I have to, I have to be careful, I take them off. I had like a brief intense"
