        "text": "So I really found my second go as being a student was much, much more successful than my first go because I enjoyed being in the classroom. I didnât feel I had to be in the classroom. So yeah, Iâd like being a teacher made me a much better student. And being a student for many, many years, my graduate degree also made me a much better teacher, I think."
