        "speaker": "A",
        "text": "So primarily, the lifestyle, I found that thatâs a great tool for recruiting because staff, they want to have a great lifestyle too. So if you can set up an office in a place like Bali, Indonesia, itâs like paradise on earth. Itâs so beautiful here, people want to join you, and so itâs great for recruiting as well."
