        "text": ". Not only is food cheaper, rent cheaper, but itâs easier to get people to help you out to do things. For example, in United States, I can't afford to pay somebody to do my laundry. Itâs too expensive. But here in Bali, I have somebody do my laundry and that saves me two hours a week."
